{"tid":1458491,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"日日去機場接機","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T17:09:37.000Z","uid":81135,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b6dcf03ab6433a8c02b4f72288ccec3e98406020","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"我地係機場只有優勢 點解大家唔好好利用？<br />\n小弟有啲愚見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1. 機場係香港命脈</strong></span><br />\n政府同警察有幾怕香港人搞機場大家都睇到<br />\n過去幾次接機都冇事發生<br />\n今日民怨沸騰個個自發去接機就流言四起<br />\n就知港府幾冇我地符 要出口術<br />\n最終點樣？除左冇航班再飛同斷左wifi外 運作一切正常<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好再人人自危喇</span><br />\n我地唔係藍絲 比不知明出處既message自亂陣腳<br />\n有時都要諗真啲係咪有人想分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2. 人數多</strong></span><br />\n人數多到幾萬人 啲狗有乜可能一次過拉哂？<br />\n就算佢話非法集結 拉埋啲遊客睇下其他國家出唔出手<br />\n非法集結罪都太模糊喇 接機都話人集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋經驗話比我地聽 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人數係保護手足既關鍵</span><br />\n點解警察成日要驅散？<br />\n因為蟻多嬲死象 <br />\n一兩隻你殺得死 一群你冇辦法 你明啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 無可能困獸鬥</span></strong><br />\n今日流言又封橋又停機鐵 講真如果佢封哂我地走唔到 只會不斷loop 驅散&gt;走唔到&gt;驅散&gt;走唔到<br />\n諗下如果警察係機場開槍/放tg 短期內仲會唔會有機飛黎香港<br />\n再者<span style=\"color: red;\"> tg唔可以係室內使用</span><br />\n到時又可以做文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>4. 真係和理飛</strong></span><br />\n機場靜坐 冇衝突 做下文宣 等<strong>香港國際機場揚威國際</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">既不失民意 又不阻民生</span><br />\n個個遊客黎到都見到咁壯觀既場面<br />\n打卡hashtag真係遍地開花<br />\n攞到國際既awareness <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 係咁和理非既情況下 <strong>有人做出過激烈行為</strong><br />\n我諗大家都識做 佢一定係鬼！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我地應該<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日日去機場接機 塞爆機場</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4f9d72d323aec1d87e92521782b278fb71e73b","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e8a17d6ce9d60d3f6b23d81133b082b2e90ab25e","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"日日和你飛"},{"pid":"259eb42ccad446c458e03018f19825c5884581f3","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"60a2086172d16fba2a2ed9e2382963201988889d","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"聽日見"},{"pid":"3282be7b32fc232c792e629dabc3fbed4555bd25","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"好想係機場見到大家"},{"pid":"23c4b3e847d3024a8a507b4ea1e60285cd217db3","tid":1458491,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n機場見大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c0618b1c5182c4f42f1d152aad8df507a4dd35","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"我要接機"},{"pid":"6338533e977fe5f2dcacad282ef09688d849a934","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"香港黑警 謀殺市民"},{"pid":"a68aa3e8016e0572808c8896632642bf8650ee01","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差 當差正仆街"},{"pid":"40333d2c9348673c0f383b0e8d16c6307e5c6e25","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:21:49.000Z","msg":"警記招：er我冇資料係手"},{"pid":"f2b46ff1009a1d044088317bcceaf97564e4e706","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"人若有良知 唔會做藍絲"},{"pid":"a32106585ba26caf72efcb9a6655329b47a69c76","tid":1458491,"uid":81135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c